                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "sbsyR",
                      "fill": "#444444",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "\"Items\" can bind to any array field. Records array = main collection with sort/filter/page size. Item-level array = nested value per record (no config). Inner elements bind to item fields (per row) or context fields (same across rows).",
